parameters: Kru "Miko-sama... please forgive our sudden visit."

Miko "Hmph... I don't think it's the visit you want forgiveness for, is
it?"
Kru "Yes... Actually, we have come with an earnest request."

Spirit of the Miko "Ahh... I thought it was something like that. You seem
to be a person of significant karma."

Spirit of the Miko "Don't you understand... Well, it's not surprising that
only we spiritual beings can comprehend. So, what is this request of
yours?"
Kru "Yes... We wish to bestow the Miko's magical power upon this Umi."
Spirit of the Miko "What? Upon this girl?"
Kru "Yes... She is the current Miko of Kuseshi."

Spirit of the Miko "It's clear she's a Miko at first glance. Hmm... And
what will she do with this magical power?"

Spirit of the Miko "Hah! Hahahaha! Young man! What grand statements you
make! To defeat Kuseshirei, a god... such talk is for sleep."
Kru "No... I am serious. I have come from the future."
Spirit of the Miko "From the future?"
Kru "Yes... There, I witnessed the world being destroyed by Kuseshirei."
Spirit of the Miko "This voice is..."
Spirit of the Miko "You are... Lady Luitesia..."
Luitesia "Yes... It's been a long time..."

Spirit of the Miko "If you are here, Lady Luitesia... what about the seal
on Kuseshirei?"

Luitesia "That's right... There's nothing holding it back now. That's why
Kuseshirei will definitely be resurrected through Umi's ritual..."

Spirit of the Miko "So we must defeat or reseal it before it becomes
untouchable. Otherwise, all our efforts in sealing it will have been for
naught... Is that what you're saying?"
Luitesia "Exactly. Please! Lend us your strength!"

Spirit of the Miko "Understood... But our magical power alone won't be
enough to oppose Kuseshirei."

Luitesia "That's fine. With your magical power, we'll break the seal on the
ruins where my divine body rests."
Luitesia "Yes... It was probably sealed by Shif long ago."

Spirit of the Miko "Because of that, Lady Luitesia's power that was
suppressing Kuseshirei's has been lost."

Luitesia "Right. So I will regain my power and together with these
children, we will defeat Kuseshirei."

Spirit of the Miko "However, to receive our power, you must overcome a
trial."
Spirit of the Miko "Our powers... gather!"
Spirit of the Miko "Now... if you desire our power, defeat us!"
Kru: "With this... I can receive power..."

Shrine Maiden's Ghost: "Ah... That girl over there... Do not waste our
power..."

Shrine Maiden's Ghost: "Phew... I'm a bit tired from going wild after so
long..."
Luitesia: "Rest easy... Leave the rest to us."

Shrine Maiden's Ghost: "I'm counting on you. Our thoughts, our power, our
wishes. I entrust them to you."
Shrine Maiden's Ghost: "Make that girl over there... happy."
Kru: "Alright! Let's go to the Mee-A ruins then!"
